Beat-maker credit required: (Beat by Current Sound)

You must credit the beat-maker by adding the text (Beat by Current Sound) to the track title as well as adding a link back from your YouTube music video to https://currentsound.com/beats as well as tag @currentsound on any social media posts using the song with the exception of TikTok which should use the different tag @currentsoundbeats. If it's dope we will share it! Please note: You must NOT write "Prod. By." you must write "Beat by" the "Prod. by" tag is strictly reserved for artists we record and direct the performance of at Current Sound in Hollywood and is only available for use only at our discretion. You must use the text (Beat by Current Sound)
